fields.name: Spectacular Spectacles
fields.description: Be the envy of your friends with these spectacular spectacles! Who's that smart-looking chief, dominating those meetings with their visionary prowess? You! (with these glasses).

fields.name: Awesome Aviators
fields.description: Lookin' good Maverick! Rock that 80s vibe with these awesome aviator shades. Because style never goes out of fashion.

fields.name: Terrific Tortoiseshell
fields.description: Style. Elegance. Vision. These terrific tortoiseshell glasses continue to the tradition and heritage of quality eyewear.

fields.name: Good Glasses
fields.description: These informal glasses are the best choice for the discerning modern businessperson.

fields.name: Fancy Fedora
fields.description: The shortcut to success in life is to look the part. And what better accessory than this stylish, yet practical, fancy fedora?

fields.name: Sneaky Sneakers
fields.description: When you want to err on the casual side of smart-casual, you'll need the perfect pair of trainers. These sneaky sneakers are the ideal finishing touch for literally any outfit.

fields.name: Nifty Knit
fields.description: Cosy. Comfortable. Red. What could be better than curling up, wrapped in this sumptuous red chunky knit? Yum yum.

fields.name: Varying Vest
fields.description: Be a dashing fashion chameleon with the varying vest. Because there's no such thing as too casual.

fields.name: Danger Denim
fields.description: Now you don't need to be a boy to be a bad boy! These stonewashed denims will strike terror in the hearts of your enemies - because only a real badass has holes in their jeans.

fields.name: Skating Slacks
fields.description: He was a boy. She was a girl. Can I make it any more obvious? Relive your youth in these skating slacks.

fields.name: Rocking Raccoon
fields.description: There's nothing as quirky or adorable than a raccoon jumper, and that's a fact!

fields.name: Perfect Pyjamas
fields.description: Yawn!! We can't wait to get to bed since we've got these brand new perfect pyjamas. Because why should kids have all the fun?

fields.name: Trendy Tee
fields.description: Have you got your tickets for the gun show? Show off the hours you've spent in the gym with this super flattering trendy tee. Grrrr!

fields.name: Wicked Wayfarers
fields.description: A style classic, these wicked wayfarers are perfect for any head shape, or level of hairiness. Phwoar!

fields.name: Dazzling Dress
fields.description: Much pretty, so wow, such dazzle. Be your most gorgeous self in this lovely dress!

fields.name: Suitable Suit
fields.description: Buy, buy, buy! Sell, sell, sell! They'll know its business time when you show up in the suitable suit. Comes complete with conveniently filofax-sized pockets.

fields.name: Joyful Jacket
fields.description: Be yourself! No pretension or artifice - if you want to wear a tracksuit top, why not. Enjoy yourself in the joyful jacket, because why should athletes have all the fun?

fields.name: Brilliant Bike
fields.description: The ultimate fashion accessory! There's nothing quite as hipster as a vintage fixie, and that's exactly what our brilliant bike gives you. Brooklyn here you come!
